      "value": "<p>Pxr light linking is using the same light linking via <strong>Data Tree's Light Bank</strong> as other Houdini lights.</p><p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544645013/lightlinking.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433136014&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544645013/lightlinking.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433136014&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544645027\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"lightlinking.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544645013\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"69c4dbd9-ebdd-4dc6-b0c1-5592a99865ea\" data-media-type=\"file\"></span></p><p> </p><p>See the Houdini documentation for more information on how to use <a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://www.sidefx.com/docs/houdini/render/lightbank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Light Bank</a>.</p><p> </p><p> </p>"
